OL,3,CConsultation underway to determine if
OL,4,Cschools should shut early
OL,6,FA Dumfries and Galloway Council
OL,7,Fconsultation into changing the
OL,8,Fstructure of the school week is
OL,9,Funderway.
OL,11,FThe proposal wants to see a four and a
OL,12,Fhalf day week introduced, with four
OL,13,Flonger days and one half day for
OL,14,Fstudents and teachers.
OL,16,FThe council say that the model is
OL,17,Fcurrently in place in other parts of
OL,18,FScotland and has the potential to
OL,19,Fimprove the education, well-being and
OL,20,Foutcomes for children and young people.
