OL,3,CConsultation underway to determine if
OL,4,Cschools should shut early
OL,6,FThey also state that the proposal
OL,7,Fwould make Dumfries and Galloway a
OL,8,Fmore attractive place for teaching
OL,9,Fstaff to apply to.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Border Dumfries and
OL,12,FGalloway Councillor Gail MacGregor
OL,13,Fsaid: "If our communities decide that
OL,14,Fit is not right and it is not going to
OL,15,Fwork for them because there is going
OL,16,Fto be some challenges.
OL,18,F"These will be around transport and
OL,19,Fchildcare if there was to be a four
OL,20,Fand a half day week.
