OL,6,F"People need to understand that first
OL,7,Fbut the primary function of this
OL,8,Fproposal is to try and ensure that we
OL,9,Fhave a better teaching offering and
OL,10,Fmore time for teachers to do the work
OL,11,Fthat is not in the classroom."
OL,13,FIn response an EIS, Educational
OL,14,FInstitute of Scotland, statement said:
OL,15,F"Education officials were unable to
OL,16,Fprovide clarity about a whole range of
OL,17,Fcontractual issues, which we would
OL,18,Fhave expected the council to have
OL,19,Fthought about before launching the
OL,20,Fconsultation."
